text: Catherine "Cathy" Mitton is a former para table tennis player who represented Great Britain. She has won team events with Sara Head and Lynne Riding. ==References== Category:Living people Category:English female table tennis players Category:Paralympic table tennis players of Great Britain Category:Medalists at the 2000 Summer Paralympics Category:Medalists at the 2004 Summer Paralympics Category:Table tennis players at the 2000 Summer Paralympics Category:Table tennis players at the 2004 Summer Paralympics Category:Table tennis players at the 2008 Summer Paralympics Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Paralympic medalists in table tennis Category:Paralympic bronze medalists for Great Britain
